data.description: Rare find in Hall County! No subdivision and no HOA!! Beautiful 3 Bedroom 2 Bath home on a full basement. This home is sitting on 1.18 Acres with access to Lake Lanier from the property. Property can be cleared to the core property for access to the cove. Seasonal views of Lake Lanier. The boat ramp at Bolding Mill is in walking distance from the home. There is a 2 car garage as well as a boat door in the basement. The home has approximately 2800+/- sq. ft. The roof was replaced in 2023. House being sold as-is.
